Aldar Gains Most in Month Ahead of CFO Announcement

-- B y   A l a a   S h a h i n e
-- 
2011-10-20T11:31:21Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-20/aldar-heads-for-biggest-gain-in-month-ahead-of-cfo-appointment.html
Aldar Properties PJSC (ALDAR)  gained the
most in a month before announcing the appointment of a chief
financial officer.  The shares advanced 2 percent, the most since Sept. 21, to
1.01 dirhams at the 2:00 p.m. close in Abu Dhabi. The benchmark
ADX General Index fell less than 0.1 percent.  Aldar said on Oct. 17 that the board of directors will
consider today appointing a replacement for Shafqat Ali Malik,
who resigned this month.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Alaa Shahine in Dubai at 
 asalha@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Shaji Mathew at 
 shajimathew@bloomberg.net  